areful RSD modeling in LAE surveys, we also seek a method to\nmitigate the additional FoG effect due to RT by making use of other information\nin a Lyman-$\\alpha$ spectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Jun 2019 17:59:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Jun 2019 08:10:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-04"}
