yzing breast cancer data, in which our method\nstrengthened levels of previously reported associations and implied the\npossibility of multiple new alleles that jointly confer breast cancer risk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Jun 2019 21:49:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Jun 2019 20:26:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-01"}
