f online job scheduling with general cost functions. Using\nthis method, we also provide a speed-augmented competitive algorithm for\nmultiple unrelated machines with convex functions $g_{ij}(t)$, where the\ncompetitive ratio depends on the curvature of cost functions $g_{ij}(t)$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Jun 2019 15:25:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 23 Aug 2020 16:54:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 15 Aug 2021 03:26:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-17"}
